criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of Diabetes mellitus;

          -  Diagnosis of Diabetic Foot;

          -  To benefit from the first assessment and follow-up at the Multidisciplinary Diabetic
             Foot Consultation of the hospitals where data collection will take place.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Presence of clinical dementia described in the patient's clinical record;

          -  Cognitive disability to answer the questionnaires;

          -  Severe visual and/or hearing impairment.
